{"tid":1056371,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"生死一線！貨車連飛2木板　後車閃避如打機","createTime":"2019-03-11T07:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T05:47:35.000Z","uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e34ef43bd1995746d89ad01b9aeed4b14fbf3cd","tid":1056371,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>生死一線！貨車連飛2木板 後車閃避如打機</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2F2ze5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2F2ze5Q&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=acebec04\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2F2ze5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190311/photo/bkn-20190311123222223-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190311140237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190311%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190311123222223-0311_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190311140237&h=02cd5cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩塊木板突然從貨車飛落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駕駛者除了要一眼關七，更要反應迅速。近日有司機在吐露港公路行駛時，險些被貨車飛落的木板擊中，情況驚險！<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」的影片可見，周一（11日）上午8時許，有貨車沿吐露港公路向大埔方向行駛時，突然有2塊木板接連從貨車車斗飄起飛落，尾隨的司機嚇得扭軚，在公路上左閃右避。<br />\n<br />\n司機事後仍驚魂未定：「我跟住佢車尾，突然飛兩塊板出來，當時好驚呀」！<br />\n<br />\n不少網民均被嚇窒：「呢個司機就真係可以告佢呀，危害其他公路駕駛者」、「記低車牌，可能後面有車中咗，死人㗎」。有網民則表示：「板一定要企側擺，先唔食風」。"},{"pid":"53439418c960f355c298ee90fda3a939ce8aab0e","tid":1056371,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"比塊野撞死有冇仇報？"},{"pid":"ffeea3d923a46d18a692297b29fd076233049ba7","tid":1056371,"uid":158601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"53439418c960f355c298ee90fda3a939ce8aab0e","tid":1056371,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"比塊野撞死有冇仇報？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"死咗仲可以點報"},{"pid":"80fb28ecce6754d58bc81038814f6176339a54ac","tid":1056371,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a4e9a9e50d45d036177f9f512e4eede5260fa1","tid":1056371,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53439418c960f355c298ee90fda3a939ce8aab0e","tid":1056371,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"比塊野撞死有冇仇報？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"做鬼仲諗報仇"},{"pid":"e3a3cc85cf88d54ca8aebe4516d2de158e44c770","tid":1056371,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"pepsi man?"},{"pid":"218a36dc2b27403872fc97a1e3048d45179113d9","tid":1056371,"uid":47500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53439418c960f355c298ee90fda3a939ce8aab0e","tid":1056371,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"比塊野撞死有冇仇報？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"連登班鍵盤車神話嘅<br />\n渣車唔識望前面架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之避唔到係你責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}